vtco.gsc.skin.info.title: Skins info
vtco.gsc.wwelol.desc: Wwelol08__ it's me, the modpack developer. Thanks for playing it!
vtco.gsc.viweda.desc: viweda is a collective image of the team's skins (wwelol08__, WhiteLight, daradanci), it's a joke. From wwelol08__ he has: color palette, glasses, hairstyle, pants, hood, gloves and symbol. From WhiteLight: glasses and hood style, clothes, symbol shape ("V"), hairstyle and shoes. With daradanci he has: lighting, being a frog, pants, tie (replaced with a scarf) and clothes under the jacket. 2 interesting facts: like WhiteLight he has a symbol written, but it's already "?" and some elements are mixed into one, for example wwelol08__ glasses with WhiteLight style or daradanci pants with wwelol08__ pants.
vtco.gsc.daradanci.desc: daradanci - a kind and good worker of Videman (not like me). Describes himself as "just a frog:)".
vtco.gsc.whitelight.desc: WhiteLight - The main boss of the team. He is Videman's ♂Dungeon Master♂. Fun fact - he has a big green "д" on his skin.
vtco.gsc.custom.desc:
custom - place for your skin! Its name "                   " will be used as the file name for the skin. To change the skin, simply drag the skin to the skins folder along the path
"<modpack folder>/config/fancymenu/assets/skins"
and enter the file name in the text field above.
